lsblk -d -o NAME,ROTA,SIZE,TYPE,MODEL
NAME ROTA  SIZE TYPE MODEL
sda     0 60.8G disk Virtual disk
sdb     0  300G disk Virtual disk
sdd     0   20G disk Virtual disk
sde     0 19.5T disk Virtual disk
sdf     0   48G disk Virtual disk
sr0     1   78K rom  VMware IDE CDR00

O means the disk is non-rotational, ssd
